Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.17,0:00:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, the time is ripe. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.20,0:00:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.90,0:00:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}keep your room brightly lit, sit \Nas far from the TV as you can,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and wait for the fated moment. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well. Everyone, \Nit's time at last.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The day has finally come {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to attempt the legendary great \Nmaneuver with Miss Layla.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.86,0:00:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all those nights I cried by myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After the many times I almost gave up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'm fine now. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The tears I want now are \Nthe tears of victory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I want to cry, I should cry after I win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After I win! After I win!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The dream everyone is looking \Nfor must be someplace{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It has to be somewhere {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:01:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until your dream comes true \Nsomeday, you're not alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Remember how I used to say \NI could make it to the end?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must have been pretending to be tough{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.90,0:01:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything I did was reckless \Nand it never got me anywhere{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But you alone were always beside me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The dream everyone is looking \Nfor must be somewhere{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can start going forward {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From this moment, something will start{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe that {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:02:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The light I haven't seen yet is \Nbeaming toward the promised place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until your dream comes true \Nsomeday, you're not alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make sure to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is ripe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You who were chosen by the stage, \Nwho overcame many ordeals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now indeed is the time to tell you \Neverything about the legendary great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must tackle the maneuver \Nwith unshakable confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary great maneuver is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:52.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"An Amazing Comeback."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.14,0:02:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that spirit of the stage \Nis there in front of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:02:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.60,0:03:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to perform the \Nlegendary great maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the players must have absolute confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After they answer that they would never die,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they are acknowledged by \Nthe spirit of the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.61,0:03:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If those two hadn't said that they \Nwould never be afraid of dying...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They would have been abandoned \Nby the spirit of the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either we would have to \Ncancel tomorrow's show,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or they'd attempt the \Nmaneuver recklessly, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the legendary great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more than I imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please make sure to rest your shoulder \Nwell in preparation for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will practice a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mia...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some suggestions concerning \Nthe stage construction for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind discussing my suggestions \Nwith the Directing Department?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it has been set in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.76,0:03:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, at last, the legendary \Ngreat maneuver will be revived
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by Layla Hamilton and Sora Naegino.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Keep that height and rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to Miss Layla's plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're going to switch to \Na trampoline after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait at the gate \Nuntil your cue to appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So all of you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the legendary great maneuver amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just built the device which \NArlon told me to build.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two... Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higher, higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marion! Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, everyone's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who was in Freedom Lights is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that even the people who \Nquit Kaleido Stage came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage is back the way it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've not seen you in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last place we met was at \Nthe Vancouver Festival, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow, I'll be on an \Nextended business trip to Asia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you make it short and \Ntell me what you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, please come to \Nsee Layla's performance tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's about selling Kaleido \NStage, I already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you want me to do something about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unfortunately, I have to tell \Nyou that you should give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I are alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to re-create the Kaleido \NStage my father envisioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I had no clue \Nwhat he was thinking at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I wasn't even trying to understand him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:06:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, are trying to avoid \Nunderstanding Layla's thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Avoiding? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a fool who could not bring \Nhimself to leave the nest
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even after his parents had left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a fool who can't acknowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that your daughter has already \Nleft the protection of your wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla is already able to fly high \Nand strong even without your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she wants you to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've been trying not to look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was my performance today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your seat is already reserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother? Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for letting you \Nknow at the last moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? How is Yume?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seats are fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already got you reserved seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the pain abated?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it stays like this, I think \NI'll be all right tomorrow too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always nervous before I go onstage,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm calm and I just \Ncan't wait until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a doctor, I couldn't possibly \Napprove of you appearing onstage,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but as a fan, I'll do \Nwhatever I can to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, are you working hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.06,0:07:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using only one arm, she can do that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:07:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all set too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then after that, the entire \Ncast will move away at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they will start the \Nlegendary great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your special stage is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally understand how you felt
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you sent my father off to the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The players who were chosen by the stage
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,cannot help but attempt the \Nlegendary great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I planned, by any means necessary,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to create a Kaleido Stage that \Ndoesn't produce any injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, in the end, I wound \Nup losing everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.48,0:09:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not finished yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will be will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should run it the way you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Originally, I planned to let Arlon \Nhandle all management-related matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I see it, I think Kaleido \NStage should belong to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your reckless method made \NSora who she is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She just dashed headlong into this herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it finally happens tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It should be around this time tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary great maneuver...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will perfect it with \NMiss Layla by any means.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The swing is longer than the \None we used for practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So watch your timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With our power,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're going to turn the \Nlegend into a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,may I ask you one question?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Fool hadn't qualified us yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what were you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never considered that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, I thought that we \Nwould be qualified by Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, come to think of it, it's \Nusually what everyone thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I'm the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them are laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yume! Have you been a good girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for inviting us, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who's supposed to thank \Nyou for coming all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just happy because if this \Nwere the old you, you would say,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I don't want to ask them \Nto come all the way here."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You used to be so reserved. Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the girl who was concerned \Nabout the hotel expenses
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and picked the flight which departed \Non the same day of the audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It made me worry more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I thought it would be all right, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you seem so lively somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it means you're confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want both of you to \Nsee my performance by all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:12:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you too, Yume.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have two more people \Nyou want to show. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have four parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll all be watching over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, you're so pushy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't say something \Nlike that and just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please reconsider selling Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already a done deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kenneth...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe I should buy it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? All by yourself? Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who are afraid to take risks
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have no choice but to walk behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You greenhorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please keep holding it tight, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.57,0:13:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we perfect the legendary great maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.89,0:13:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the audience will come back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they do, let's create \Na wonderful show again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A real show which both children \Nand adults can enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kate, how are Sora and everybody doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The potential for unlimited possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The upright Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door to the future will open \Nto those fools who are not afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like they don't have any lifelines.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Then if they drop...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to create the \Nbest show with Miss Layla.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I'm getting chills.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so far, but it looks \Nlike it's so close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to focus only on Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jump toward Miss Layla... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're flying. Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you have wings on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They finally made the legend reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not scared at all. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm with Miss Layla. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.59,0:16:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so happy. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel like crying. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wish I could keep performing \Nlike this forever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The brilliance of life that \Ndoesn't flinch at anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is indeed the legendary great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.09,0:17:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only is the legendary great \Nmaneuver a dangerous maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it is also an expression of a strong \Nlife that keeps even death at bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The maneuver which even gives the \Naudience the strength to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.69,0:17:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what the legendary great maneuver was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder someone like me was \Nunable to get in their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The swing is farther than it's \Nsupposed to be because of the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it with all our might.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, dim the lighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No buts. Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Sora, you're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing. It was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen anything like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.11,0:18:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm still flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.18,0:19:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a wonderful show.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I understand what Yuri said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.25,0:19:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can fly anywhere with your own \Nwings without my help anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hurt your shoulder?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I won't be able to appear \Non Kaleido Stage anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not true, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.26,0:19:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kate already told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, I didn't want to miss this chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I staged the best performance with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And received the best applause.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't ask anything more \Nfor my last performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... but... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.39,0:20:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.13,0:21:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to perfect the legendary \Ngreat maneuver with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I prepared myself to pay any price.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.44,0:21:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,didn't you tell me that you \Nwould challenge fate with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If what you told me is really true,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stand up, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to be my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be my dream, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.30,0:22:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be Miss Layla's dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.73,0:22:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.17,0:22:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you can become a true Kaleido Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A true Kaleido Star...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.72,0:22:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm here between the sky and the \Nroads, and facing against the wind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.45,0:22:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I'm facing forward so the sorrow \Ndoesn't rain down ever again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.28,0:22:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I came all the way here after \NI jumped over that wall{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.30,0:22:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are many times when \NI just want to run away{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.64,0:22:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'm still here, so, \NI'm not daunted that much{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The poem I scribbled down, I can just \Nstart writing over from the beginning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.49,0:23:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unable to write it well, I'm laughing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.24,0:23:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.12,0:23:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.16,0:23:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla, I will become a true \NKaleido Star no matter what!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.37,0:23:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will! I will!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.88,0:23:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will work harder and harder! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.40,0:23:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hi, everyone! I am Sora Naegino.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.93,0:23:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How was the legendary great maneuver \Nwhich I did with Miss Layla?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.89,0:23:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was so tough. I worked so \Nhard. And I cried so much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.61,0:23:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I am Miss Layla's dream, \Nand Miss Layla's dream is me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.88,0:23:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll definitely become a true Kaleido \NStar, for Miss Layla's sake as well!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.87,0:23:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will! I will!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.55,0:24:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time on Kaleido Star, "Amazing \NPrologue To Stardom, part 1."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.37,0:24:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My wings are my dream and on towards the sky.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.21,0:24:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
